node.text: I’m so pleased to be awarded the @prettylittlething LGBTQ+ Supporter of the year award! It’s so important to me to support and be an example for everyone to live there life authentically! You can watch the At Home Awards show on @prettylittlething Instagram LIVE Right now, to see the other amazing winners of the #prettylittlethingawards

node.text: Always so good to meet with small business owners in California

Only four times in U.S. history has a recall effort against a governor garnered enough signatures to force an election like this one. #RecallGavinNewsom USA TODAY Politics @usatodayDC 1h The list of challengers includes reality star Caitlyn Jenner, radio host Larry Elder and the state's 2018 Republican gubernatorial nominee John Cox. 12:21 PM 8/5/21 Twitter for iPhone 39 11'.

node.text: I get this question every day since I’ve started this campaign to Save California! This is a rare opportunity to remove corrupt power from CA

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Caitlyn Jenner on August 03, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'How the competition stacks up Campaign contributions come in three flavors: itemized donations, from people who give more than $100, anonymous small dollar contributions from people who gave less than that and unlimited money from self-funded candidates All Donations Self-funded Small dollar Caitlyn Jenner Kevin Paffrath Jenny Rae Le Roux Kevin Kiley Larry Elder $0 $50,000 $100,000 $150,000 $200,000 Source: California Secretary of State Analysis by CalMatters. node.text: Beyond proud of the support we have received from the grassroots! We have the most small dollar donors of all candidates. I’m representing the every day Californian

node.text: BREAKING: TODAY WE WON! Newsom v. Weber. I held our governor accountable and will continue to expose the hypocrisy, lies, and corruption in Sacramento. Join the movement link in bio.

node.text: It’s time for WE THE PEOPLE to hold our corrupt politicians in Sacramento accountable. Nobody should be above the law. Especially our governor

node.text: No wonder he is being recalled. Out with the old career politicians and special interests. I am going to Sacramento to fight for ALL Californians, not lobbyists. Get involved link in bio.
